metadata.description: Human-labeled fit scores (0-100) for resume-JD pairs

scoring_criteria.90-100: Excellent match - meets or exceeds all requirements
scoring_criteria.70-89: Good match - meets most requirements with minor gaps
scoring_criteria.50-69: Moderate match - has some relevant skills but significant gaps
scoring_criteria.0-29: Poor match - does not meet key requirements
